ruby-clamav
-------------------------------------------
Ruby bindings for Clam AntiVirus.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.5.25-7
  libclamav2-0.91.2-1
  ruby-1.8.6-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding devel packages)
  cygwin-1.5.25-7
  binutils-20060817-1
  cygport-0.3.7-1
  gcc-core-3.4.4-3
  make-3.81-1

Canonical homepage:
  http://raa.ruby-lang.org/project/clamavr/

Canonical download:
  http://www.moonwolf.com/ruby/archive/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack ruby-clamav-0.2.0-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./ruby-clamav-0.2.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/ruby-clamav-0.2.0-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/ruby-clamav-0.2.0-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

  /usr/lib/ruby/site_ruby/1.8/i386-cygwin/clamav.so
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/ruby-clamav-0.2.0.README
  /usr/share/doc/ruby-clamav-0.2.0/README

------------------

Port Notes:

